Package: demovuln
Type: Package
Title: Demographic Vulnerability Metrics for Matrix Population Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Alex", family = "Gimenez-Romero", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "alexeltsar8@gmail.com"))
Description: Simulates temporally structured perturbations acting on matrix
    population models and computes population reduction and integrated
    vulnerability metrics across perturbation regimes. This R implementation is
    intended as a lightweight companion to the Python package 'demovuln'.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
